metadata.name: The Pullback
metadata.description:
A sign of fear or a sign of respect. In this case I image a little bit of both.

This shot was taken on Dec 4th 2020 at Noriega Street in Ocean Beach, San Francisco.

The beach was a party at first light as locals watched their peers paddle into San Francisco's Monsters.

Taken on Fuji XPro1 with a vintage 300mm Yashica lens and adapter.
